  m_Text: Both the cube and the timer are reading from the data asset individually-
    neither of them having dependancies on anything else in the scene for their functionality.
    Additionally both of them can be switched to using constant values anytime instead
    of data referencing. Try editing the value of DataExample to see how the cube
    and timer update whilst running the editor, and how the changes are not forgotten.
